reviewText: I would have liked to see a little more content but it had some really good techniques that I had not seen before on basic level lomi lomi techniques.  I'm glad I bought it.

This instructional cd was very easy to follow and had wonderful new moves I could incorporate into my existing Lomi mssage routine.
I would highly recommend it.
This is an excellent overview of Lomi Lomi. It's very easy for massage therapists to incorporate Lomi Lomi into their routine.
